title: Chris Teti from The World Is… and Silver Bullet Studios
itunes:title: Chris Teti from The World Is… and Silver Bullet Studios
description:
My new friend Chris Teti from The World Is...and Silver Bullet Studios ducks into the podcast this week with amazing results! We dive into DIY transitions, eclectic music tastes and why his grandmother thinks tour is like American Idol. Joking aside, Chris is a very devoted dude to the DIY music scene and I hope you enjoy the conversation!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
